#: ../../integrations/comfyui_rh_voxcpm.rst:3 499ebc22f5954c8ebf46c5768812495b
msgid "ComfyUI_RH_VoxCPM"
msgstr "ComfyUI_RH_VoxCPM"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_rh_voxcpm.rst:5 fd029fdcd5454c03b50be6dc606d7a21
msgid ""
"ComfyUI_RH_VoxCPM is a community-maintained ComfyUI integration for "
"VoxCPM with native **VoxCPM 2** support, multi-speaker dialogue "
"generation, optional LoRA loading, automatic ASR for cloning workflows, "
"and reference-audio denoising."
msgstr ""
"ComfyUI_RH_VoxCPM 是一个由社区维护的 ComfyUI 集成项目，面向 VoxCPM，支持原生 **VoxCPM 2**、"
"多人对话生成、可选 LoRA 加载、克隆流程中的自动 ASR，以及参考音频去噪。"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_rh_voxcpm.rst:9 1fc5f51beb0e4eea90ec773553a1bf83
msgid ""
"Repo: `HM-RunningHub/ComfyUI_RH_VoxCPM <https://github.com/HM-"
"RunningHub/ComfyUI_RH_VoxCPM>`_"
msgstr ""
"仓库：`HM-RunningHub/ComfyUI_RH_VoxCPM <https://github.com/HM-RunningHub/ComfyUI_RH_VoxCPM>`_"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_rh_voxcpm.rst:10 17d86ebaf5314ee5aa27ffb94e52771c
msgid "Try online: `RunningHub <https://www.runninghub.ai/?inviteCode=rh-v1367>`_"
msgstr "在线体验：`RunningHub <https://www.runninghub.ai/?inviteCode=rh-v1367>`_"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_rh_voxcpm.rst:14 a53b76d5967c4a98a05e4abf736dc5b8
msgid ""
"This project is maintained by the community, not by OpenBMB. For the "
"other ComfyUI integrations in the ecosystem, see :doc:`comfyui_voxcpm` "
"and :doc:`comfyui_voxcpmtts`."
msgstr ""
"该项目由社区维护，并非 OpenBMB 官方维护。若想查看生态中的其他 ComfyUI 集成，请参阅 :doc:`comfyui_voxcpm` "
"和 :doc:`comfyui_voxcpmtts`。"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_rh_voxcpm.rst:18 0c66b41ba0d04af686274dc0934cfa72
msgid "Supported VoxCPM Versions"
msgstr "支持的 VoxCPM 版本"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_rh_voxcpm.rst:22 9ed6615b3e87467cbf4a015ba81596b0
msgid "VoxCPM 2"
msgstr "VoxCPM 2"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_rh_voxcpm.rst:23 db6ae29455d74931a3e782b3d695e820
msgid ""
"✅ Recommended. Full feature set including Ultimate Cloning and multi-"
"speaker workflows."
msgstr "✅ 推荐。具备完整功能集，包括 Ultimate Cloning 和多人工作流。"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_rh_voxcpm.rst:24 15b5d19b9f184e68b70db0eaf791c609
msgid "VoxCPM 1.5"
msgstr "VoxCPM 1.5"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_rh_voxcpm.rst:25 71156339cab44a5a8510e316bb3172b2
msgid "✅ Supported through the shared loader workflow."
msgstr "✅ 通过共享的加载节点工作流提供支持。"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_rh_voxcpm.rst:26 f8ed57286fb7487da2469f53e2cc3d8f
msgid "VoxCPM-0.5B"
msgstr "VoxCPM-0.5B"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_rh_voxcpm.rst:27 aabac72836c74e6682516ecf89777d06
msgid "✅ Supported as a lighter-weight option."
msgstr "✅ 作为更轻量的选项提供支持。"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_rh_voxcpm.rst:30 4d8d9c6b48b84a3b98fcc68ef63aaffd
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概览"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_rh_voxcpm.rst:32 597362fce924454d9c7fbde14d3ee549
msgid "The integration exposes three main nodes:"
msgstr "该集成提供三个主要节点："

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_rh_voxcpm.rst:34 6a8f1d04e0ee44ef93061459b59188d4
msgid ""
"**RunningHub VoxCPM Load Model** — load a local VoxCPM model directory "
"from ``ComfyUI/models/voxcpm/`` with optional LoRA weights"
msgstr ""
"**RunningHub VoxCPM Load Model**：从 ``ComfyUI/models/voxcpm/`` 加载本地 VoxCPM 模型目录，"
"并可选加载 LoRA 权重"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_rh_voxcpm.rst:36 ae4b7c17313441acae6d2991943cf305
msgid ""
"**RunningHub VoxCPM Generate Speech** — a single generation node covering"
" Voice Design, Controllable Cloning, and Ultimate Cloning"
msgstr ""
"**RunningHub VoxCPM Generate Speech**：一个统一的生成节点，覆盖 Voice Design、"
"Controllable Cloning 和 Ultimate Cloning"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_rh_voxcpm.rst:38 1574b676422c4ad9bea4de9b9f5d3f4a
msgid ""
"**RunningHub VoxCPM Multi-Speaker** — generate tagged multi-speaker "
"dialogue for up to five speakers with per-speaker voice control"
msgstr ""
"**RunningHub VoxCPM Multi-Speaker**：生成带标签的多人对话，最多支持五个说话人，并可为每个说话人单独控制音色"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_rh_voxcpm.rst:41 692338190c324aaaa2f0d95fef839dcc
msgid ""
"Compared with other ComfyUI ecosystem options, this project is currently "
"the most feature-complete visual workflow for VoxCPM 2 in the docs set: "
"it combines native V2 support, multi-speaker generation, optional LoRA "
"loading, auto-ASR, and ZipEnhancer-based denoising in one package."
msgstr ""
"相较于文档中列出的其他 ComfyUI 生态方案，这个项目目前是对 VoxCPM 2 支持最完整的可视化工作流之一："
"它把原生 V2 支持、多人生成、可选 LoRA 加载、自动 ASR 与基于 ZipEnhancer 的去噪整合在同一个包中。"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_rh_voxcpm.rst:47 9995250b3d9242c2bb7c1ac75fc58f17
msgid "Features"
msgstr "特性"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_rh_voxcpm.rst:49 609aeeb64a614562851e23b09ed45953
msgid "**Voice Design** from a text-only control instruction"
msgstr "通过纯文本控制指令实现 **Voice Design**"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_rh_voxcpm.rst:50 f78a710fec8b4d1a916b4c3f6d1e9ec3
msgid "**Controllable Cloning** from reference audio with optional style guidance"
msgstr "通过参考音频进行 **Controllable Cloning**，并可选加入风格控制"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_rh_voxcpm.rst:51 8ab2ea881bbe4715aa1be5a1fb75f495
msgid ""
"**Ultimate Cloning** for prompt continuation / maximum fidelity (**VoxCPM"
" 2 only**)"
msgstr "**Ultimate Cloning**：用于 prompt 延续 / 极致还原（**仅限 VoxCPM 2**）"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_rh_voxcpm.rst:52 455fd430007a4ace93b99ba801776601
msgid "**LoRA loading** from ``ComfyUI/models/voxcpm/loras/``"
msgstr "从 ``ComfyUI/models/voxcpm/loras/`` 加载 **LoRA**"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_rh_voxcpm.rst:53 39a1bc6ffa294d97bc7ff0c13fdbc3d6
msgid ""
"**Automatic ASR** via FunASR SenseVoiceSmall when "
"``reference_audio_text`` is empty in Ultimate Cloning"
msgstr ""
"当 Ultimate Cloning 模式下 ``reference_audio_text`` 为空时，通过 FunASR SenseVoiceSmall "
"执行 **自动 ASR**"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_rh_voxcpm.rst:54 fa31af91786d40ed9c102f774a3e2524
msgid "**Reference denoising** via ZipEnhancer before cloning"
msgstr "在克隆前通过 ZipEnhancer 对参考音频进行 **去噪**"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_rh_voxcpm.rst:55 dd9c615b6038429e8e167196073aeca5
msgid ""
"**Multi-speaker dialogue** from tagged scripts such as ``[spk1]... "
"[spk2]...``"
msgstr "从 ``[spk1]... [spk2]...`` 这类带标签脚本生成 **多人对话**"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_rh_voxcpm.rst:56 1651fa837ef14656a63b80e57ac3557f
msgid ""
"**Example workflows** included in the repository for both single-speaker "
"and multi-speaker generation"
msgstr "仓库内自带单人生成和多人生成的 **示例工作流**"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_rh_voxcpm.rst:59 75c7e23f5cf0409599bf504bdc285634
msgid "Prerequisites"
msgstr "前置要求"

