msgstr ""
"如果你希望使用自动转写，需要将 SenseVoiceSmall 放在 "
"``ComfyUI/models/SenseVoice/SenseVoiceSmall/`` 下"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_rh_voxcpm.rst:64 125b4f59b6ce407dbb3cc841ba730f17
msgid ""
"ZipEnhancer available under "
"``ComfyUI/models/voxcpm/speech_zipenhancer_ans_multiloss_16k_base/`` if "
